Package org.eclipse.mat.inspections.collectionextract

package org.eclipse.mat.inspections.collectionextract
Code for reading data from collections found in a snapshot. This allows queries to be written to operate on collections in a snapshot without depending on the actual implementation of the collection.
Since:
1.5
